        <p>Houzz Pro and Buildertrend are both excellent platforms for residential contractors. Buildertrend is the more complete project management system. But Houzz Pro has a unique card to play: it puts your business in front of homeowners actively looking for contractors. This comparison examines when that advantage tips the decision.</p>

        <h2>Quick comparison</h2>
